%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Mentalism Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

A caster with access to the mentalism domain is generally more aware of the powers of his mind than others are of theirs. He is able to see for a short bit into the future with the aid of this domain as well as some distance away.

Clerics with the Mentalism Domain gain a +1 caster level bonus when casting abjuration sphere spells.

The mentalism domain contains the following spells:

Confusion, Detect Thoughts, Clairvoyance, Modify Memory, Telepathic Bond, Bolt of Force, Mind Blank, Inner Eye, Astral Projection

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Cevahir

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
